---
import Base from "@/layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base 
 title="Services" 
 description="AI Enablement, FinOps, Virtual DevOps & SRE, and Virtual CISO services for small and mid-sized businesses."
>
 <!-- Page Header -->
 <section class="section bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50">
  <div class="container">
   <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
    <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-extrabold">
     Services Built for Growing Businesses
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-body dark:text-darkmode-body">
     Flexible engagement models. Senior expertise. No bloated retainers.
    </p>
   </div>
  </div>
 </section>

 <!-- AI Enablement -->
 <section id="ai-enablement" class="section scroll-mt-24">
  <div class="container">
   <div class="grid items-start gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
    <div>
     <div class="mb-4 flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-secondary/10 text-secondary">
      <svg class="h-7 w-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
       <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z" />
      </svg>
     </div>
     <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold">AI Enablement</h2>
     <p class="mt-2 text-xs font-medium text-secondary">Make sense of AI. Put it to work.</p>
     
     <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-body dark:text-darkmode-body">
      <p>
       AI is everywhere — but most businesses are stuck between "we should do something with AI" and "we have no idea where to start."
      </p>
      <p>
       We cut through the noise and help you identify high-impact use cases, evaluate tools without vendor bias, and implement workflows that actually integrate with your existing systems.
      </p>
     </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="card">
     <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-dark dark:text-white">What We Help With</h3>
     <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
       <svg class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-secondary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
       </svg>
       <span class="text-body dark:text-darkmode-body">Identify high-impact AI use cases specific to your business</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
       <svg class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-secondary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
       </svg>
       <span class="text-body dark:text-darkmode-body">Evaluate tools and platforms without vendor bias</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
       <svg class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-secondary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
       </svg>
       <span class="text-body dark:text-darkmode-body">Implement AI workflows that integrate with your existing systems</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
       <svg class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-secondary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
       </svg>
       <span class="text-body dark:text-darkmode-body">Train your team to use AI tools effectively and safely</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
       <svg class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-secondary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
       </svg>
       <span class="text-body dark:text-darkmode-body">Establish governance and policies for responsible AI use</span>
      </li>
     </ul>
    </div>
   </div>
  </div>
 </section>

 <!-- Divider -->
 <div class="container"><hr class="border-border dark:border-darkmode-border" /></div>

 <!-- DevOps & SRE -->
 <section id="devops-sre" class="section scroll-mt-24">
  <div class="container">
   <div class="grid items-start gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
    <div class="lg:order-2">
     <div class="mb-4 flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-primary/10 text-primary dark:text-darkmode-primary">
      <svg class="h-7 w-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
       <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15" />
      </svg>
     </div>
     <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold">Virtual DevOps & Site Reliability Engineering</h2>
     <p class="mt-2 text-xs font-medium text-primary dark:text-darkmode-primary">Reliable systems. Faster delivery. Less noise.</p>
     
     <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-body dark:text-darkmode-body">
      <p>
       You need modern infrastructure practices, but a full-time DevOps or SRE hire might be overkill — or impossible to find.
      </p>
      <p>
       Our virtual engineering services give you access to senior talent who've migrated hundreds of services to Kubernetes, reduced monthly alerts from 1,000+ to under 50, and built disaster recovery programs that actually work when you need them.
      </p>
     </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="card lg:order-1">
     <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-dark dark:text-white">What We Help With</h3>
     <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
       <svg class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-primary dark:text-darkmode-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
       </svg>
       <span class="text-body dark:text-darkmode-body">Design and implement CI/CD pipelines (GitHub Actions, Jenkins, ArgoCD)</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
       <svg class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-primary dark:text-darkmode-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
       </svg>
       <span class="text-body dark:text-darkmode-body">Build infrastructure as code with Terraform, AWS CDK, or Helm</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
       <svg class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-primary dark:text-darkmode-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
       </svg>
       <span class="text-body dark:text-darkmode-body">Architect Kubernetes deployments and container strategies</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
       <svg class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-primary dark:text-darkmode-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
       </svg>
       <span class="text-body dark:text-darkmode-body">Implement observability (Prometheus, Grafana, Datadog)</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
       <svg class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-primary dark:text-darkmode-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
       </svg>
       <span class="text-body dark:text-darkmode-body">Establish SLIs, SLOs, and incident response processes</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
       <svg class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-primary dark:text-darkmode-primary" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
       </svg>
       <span class="text-body dark:text-darkmode-body">Reduce alert fatigue and conduct blameless post-mortems</span>
      </li>
     </ul>
    </div>
   </div>
  </div>
 </section>

 <!-- Divider -->
 <div class="container"><hr class="border-border dark:border-darkmode-border" /></div>

 <!-- FinOps -->
 <section id="finops" class="section scroll-mt-24">
  <div class="container">
   <div class="grid items-start gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
    <div class="lg:order-2">
     <div class="mb-4 flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-amber-500/10 text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400">
      <svg class="h-7 w-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
       <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
      </svg>
     </div>
     <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold">FinOps & Cloud Cost Optimization</h2>
     <p class="mt-2 text-xs font-medium text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400">Reduce cloud spend without sacrificing performance.</p>
     
     <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-body dark:text-darkmode-body">
      <p>
       Cloud costs can spiral out of control — especially when you're scaling fast. But cutting costs blindly can break things or slow you down.
      </p>
      <p>
       Our FinOps services evaluate your existing deployments to identify real cost savings opportunities. We analyze your infrastructure, usage patterns, and billing data to find waste, optimize resource sizing, and recommend changes that reduce spend while maintaining or improving performance.
      </p>
     </div>

     <!-- Guarantee -->
     <div class="mt-8 rounded-xl border-2 border-amber-500/30 bg-amber-50/50 p-6 dark:border-amber-400/30 dark:bg-amber-900/10">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
       <div class="flex-shrink-0">
        <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
         <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
        </svg>
       </div>
       <div>
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-amber-900 dark:text-amber-200">Our Guarantee</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-amber-800 dark:text-amber-300">
         If we don't save you more than our billable hours, you don't pay. We're confident in our ability to find real cost savings in your cloud infrastructure.
        </p>
       </div>
      </div>
     </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="card lg:order-1">
     <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-dark dark:text-white">What We Help With</h3>
     <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
       <svg class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
       </svg>
       <span class="text-body dark:text-darkmode-body">Comprehensive cloud cost audits and spend analysis</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
       <svg class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
       </svg>
       <span class="text-body dark:text-darkmode-body">Identify and eliminate unused or underutilized resources</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
       <svg class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
       </svg>
       <span class="text-body dark:text-darkmode-body">Right-size compute, storage, and database resources</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
       <svg class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
       </svg>
       <span class="text-body dark:text-darkmode-body">Optimize reserved instances, savings plans, and spot instances</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
       <svg class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
       </svg>
       <span class="text-body dark:text-darkmode-body">Implement cost allocation and chargeback strategies</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
       <svg class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
       </svg>
       <span class="text-body dark:text-darkmode-body">Establish FinOps practices and cost monitoring dashboards</span>
      </li>
     </ul>
    </div>
   </div>
  </div>
 </section>

 <!-- Divider -->
 <div class="container"><hr class="border-border dark:border-darkmode-border" /></div>

 <!-- Virtual CISO -->
 <section id="virtual-ciso" class="section scroll-mt-24">
  <div class="container">
   <div class="grid items-start gap-12 lg:grid-cols-2">
    <div>
     <div class="mb-4 flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-green-500/10 text-green-600 dark:text-green-400">
      <svg class="h-7 w-7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
       <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
      </svg>
     </div>
     <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold">Virtual CISO & Information Security</h2>
     <p class="mt-2 text-xs font-medium text-green-600 dark:text-green-400">Security leadership without the full-time cost.</p>
     
     <div class="mt-6 space-y-4 text-body dark:text-darkmode-body">
      <p>
       Growing businesses face real security risks — but rarely have the budget for a dedicated CISO. Our virtual CISO services give you experienced security leadership on a flexible retainer.
      </p>
      <p>
       Our founder holds an active CISSP (since 2017) and has served in acting CISO roles, working directly with executives while remaining hands-on with technical implementation.
      </p>
     </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="card">
     <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-dark dark:text-white">What We Help With</h3>
     <ul class="mt-4 space-y-3">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
       <svg class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-green-600 dark:text-green-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
       </svg>
       <span class="text-body dark:text-darkmode-body">Develop and maintain security policies and programs</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
       <svg class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-green-600 dark:text-green-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
       </svg>
       <span class="text-body dark:text-darkmode-body">Achieve and maintain compliance (SOC2, FINRA, SEC, SOX)</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
       <svg class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-green-600 dark:text-green-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
       </svg>
       <span class="text-body dark:text-darkmode-body">Conduct risk assessments and threat modeling</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
       <svg class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-green-600 dark:text-green-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
       </svg>
       <span class="text-body dark:text-darkmode-body">Manage vulnerability programs and penetration testing</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
       <svg class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-green-600 dark:text-green-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
       </svg>
       <span class="text-body dark:text-darkmode-body">Implement Zero Trust architectures and cloud security</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
       <svg class="mt-1 h-5 w-5 flex-shrink-0 text-green-600 dark:text-green-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
       </svg>
       <span class="text-body dark:text-darkmode-body">Respond to security incidents and prepare for audits</span>
      </li>
     </ul>
    </div>
   </div>
  </div>
 </section>

 <!-- Engagement Models -->
 <section class="section bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800/50">
  <div class="container">
   <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-center">
    <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold">Flexible Engagement Models</h2>
    <p class="mt-4 text-body dark:text-darkmode-body">
     We work on monthly retainers tailored to your needs — not one-size-fits-all packages.
    </p>
   </div>

   <div class="mt-12 grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
    <div class="card text-center">
     <div class="mx-auto mb-4 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary dark:text-darkmode-primary">
      <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
       <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4" />
      </svg>
     </div>
     <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">Discovery</h3>
     <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-body dark:text-darkmode-body">
      2-4 week assessment of your current environment, risks, and opportunities. Deliverable: prioritized roadmap.
     </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card text-center">
     <div class="mx-auto mb-4 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary dark:text-darkmode-primary">
      <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
       <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
