     </div>
     <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">Ongoing Retainer</h3>
     <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-body dark:text-darkmode-body">
      Monthly hours allocated to advisory, implementation, and support. Scale up or down as needs change.
     </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card text-center">
     <div class="mx-auto mb-4 flex h-12 w-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-primary/10 text-primary dark:text-darkmode-primary">
      <svg class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
       <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4" />
      </svg>
     </div>
     <h3 class="text-lg font-bold">Project-Based</h3>
     <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-body dark:text-darkmode-body">
      Defined-scope projects like compliance preparation, cloud migration, or tool implementation.
     </p>
    </div>
   </div>

   <div class="mt-12 text-center">
    <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">
     Let's Design Your Engagement
     <svg class="ml-2 h-5 w-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3" />
     </svg>
